# ===================================================================
# Local Development Quick Start:
# ===================================================================
# 1. Ensure Docker is running
# 2. Copy this file: cp .env.local.example .env.local
# 3. Start local Supabase: pnpm supabase:start
# 4. Copy the URLs and keys from the output to your .env.local
# 5. Run migrations: pnpm db:migrate  
# 6. Start development: pnpm dev:local (or just pnpm dev if Supabase is already running)
# ===================================================================